Class Stream<T>

  • java.lang.Object

    java.io.Serializable

    public class Stream<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The basic class used by an end-user of this API. Represents a stream of data and exposes multiple operators to compose complex dataflows.
